(x - 1)^{p-1} = \sum_{k = 0}^{p-1} \binom{p - 1}{k}(-1)^{p - 1 - k}x^k
\binom{p - 1}{k} = (-1)^k
(-1)^{p - 1 - k} = (-1)^k
(x - 1)^{p-1} = \sum_{k = 0}^{p-1}x^k.
